    Class Description
    AbstractLoaderoService
    This abstract class serves as a template for each service layer, that should be implemented for each Loadero model in order to provide CRUD operations.
    Labeled
    Interface to define specific behaviour for every Loadero enum type, that are used to set Loadero's parameters such as network conditions, test mode etc.
    LoaderoBrowserType
    Enum to define browser types provided for usage in Loadero.
    LoaderoClient
    Main entry point of the interaction with the Loadero API.
    LoaderoClientInternalException  
    LoaderoCommonOperation<T extends LoaderoModel>
    Public interface for specifying common operation for Loadero service layer such as GET request and method for building urls.
    LoaderoComputeUnitsType
    Enum to define compute units types provided for usage in Loadero.
    LoaderoGroup
    LoaderoGroup class is responsible for representing information retrieved from Loadero API /groups/groupId endpoint.
    LoaderoHttpException  
    LoaderoIncrementStrategyType
    Enum to define increment strategies types provided for usage in Loadero.
    LoaderoLocationType
    Enum to define location types provided for usage in Loadero.
    LoaderoMediaType
    Enum to define media types provided for usage in Loadero.
    LoaderoModel
    Simple marker interface to mark Loadero related classes together.
    LoaderoModelType
    Enum types are used for creation/validation of concrete LoaderoModel classes.
    LoaderoNetworkType
    Enum to define network condition types provided for usage in Loadero.
    LoaderoParticipant
    LoaderoParticipant class is responsible to represent information retrieved/updated from/to Loadero API /participants/participantId endpoint.
    LoaderoRunInfo
    LoaderoRunInfo class is responsible for representing retrieved information during and after test runs.
    LoaderoScriptFileLoc
    LoaderoScriptFileLoc purpose is to store information about Loadero test script, that is used to run tests.
    LoaderoSpecialOperation<T extends LoaderoModel>
    Public interface to provide not so common operation for each service layer.
    LoaderoTestModeType
    Enum to define test mode types provided for usage in Loadero.
    LoaderoTestOptions
    LoaderoTestDescription object is a configuration profile to specify test parameters for creation of Loadero tests.
    LoaderoTestRunParticipantResult
    LoaderoTestRunParticipantResult represents the information about single participant test run result.
    LoaderoTestRunResult
    LoaderoTestRunResult class represents the information retrieved from Loadero /runs/:runID/results/.
